@node Environment Variables
@chapter Environment Variables

@section Run time (read by the produced binary)

@table @env
@item OCI2BIN_DEBUG
Any value enables verbose runtime diagnostics (same as @option{--debug}).
@item OCI2BIN_TMPDIR
Directory for the runtime extraction tmpdir; tried before @env{TMPDIR}.
Point at a tmpfs for speed and to keep the rootfs off disk.
@item TMPDIR
Fallback extraction directory (then @file{/tmp}, then @file{/var/tmp}).
@item OCI2BIN_IDENTITY
Path to the age identity (or SSH private key) used to decrypt an
@option{--encrypt} recipient image.
@item OCI2BIN_PASSWORD / OCI2BIN_PASSWORD_FILE
Passphrase (or a file whose first line is the passphrase) for a
@option{--passphrase} image.
@item OCI2BIN_CDI_DIR
Extra directory searched first for CDI specs, ahead of @file{/etc/cdi}
and @file{/run/cdi} (@option{--gpus} / @option{--cdi-device}).
@item SSH_AUTH_SOCK
Path to the SSH agent socket forwarded when @option{--ssh-agent} is
given.
@item HOME
Base for the named-container state directory
(@file{~/.cache/oci2bin/containers/}).
@end table

@section Build time (read by the oci2bin CLI)

@table @env
@item OCI2BIN_HOME
Override the directory where shared resources are found
(@file{build_polyglot.py}, pre-built loader binaries).  Set
automatically by @command{make install} to
@file{@var{PREFIX}/share/oci2bin}.
@item AARCH64_SYSROOT / X86_64_SYSROOT
Override the sysroot used by the aarch64 / x86_64 cross-compiler.
aarch64 default: @file{/usr/aarch64-redhat-linux/sys-root/fc43}.
@item SOURCE_DATE_EPOCH
Fixed timestamp for @option{--reproducible} / @option{--offline-only}
builds.
@item VM_CPUS / VM_MEM_MB
Default vCPU count and memory (MiB) baked into a VM-mode binary.
@item XDG_CACHE_HOME / XDG_DATA_HOME
Override @file{~/.cache} (build/layer caches) and @file{~/.local/share}
(detached-stack manifests, freeze tokens).
@end table

@c ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
@node Files
@chapter Files

@table @file
@item ~/.cache/oci2bin/
Per-image build cache used by @option{--cache}.  Each entry is a
directory named @file{@var{image}_@var{digest}/} containing the output
binary.
@item /proc/self/exe
The loader opens this path to read its embedded OCI data at runtime.
@item @var{PREFIX}/bin/oci2bin
The CLI wrapper script installed by @command{make install}.
@item @var{PREFIX}/share/oci2bin/build/loader-x86_64
Pre-compiled static loader for x86_64.
@item @var{PREFIX}/share/oci2bin/build/loader-aarch64
Pre-compiled static loader for aarch64.
@item @var{PREFIX}/share/oci2bin/scripts/build_polyglot.py
Polyglot builder script.
@item @var{PREFIX}/share/oci2bin/src/loader.c
Loader source code.
@end table

